<br>
Shaman it's an easy fight though.  Slow him, buff/haste yourself/pet.  Epic DoT, JBB, and maybe throw a random DoT on him.  Start meleeing.  Keep the JBB going, with pet and the DoT's.  If you get low, torpor yourself.  It's a simplistic fight.<br>
<br>
For a Druid though...Just not gonna happen, our pet doesn't have the damage output of a Shamans, we can't take the damage, nor can we slow, and we haven't got that many DoT's/manaless nukes. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=63622">Xican's crappy profile</a>
